  "detailed_description": "🐤The most love-filled, <strong>survivor-based shooter</strong> in Steam history is here!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/f401ba787f66eb4dcb297b0378ed11b6.poster.avif?t=1740819080\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/f401ba787f66eb4dcb297b0378ed11b6.webm?t=1740819080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/f401ba787f66eb4dcb297b0378ed11b6.mp4?t=1740819080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🤗The goal of this game is to <strong>bind</strong> this rebellious cutie in a hug!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/19a4cedea8937b37ba25f7d0d33f3bb8.poster.avif?t=1740819080\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/19a4cedea8937b37ba25f7d0d33f3bb8.webm?t=1740819080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/19a4cedea8937b37ba25f7d0d33f3bb8.mp4?t=1740819080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🍅The hero has no ability to fight. But he can <strong>hug</strong> and love his friends!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/a61c502f3cb6d0720051b56ed431afcc.poster.avif?t=1740819080\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271940/extras/a61c502f3cb6d0720051b56ed431afcc.webm?t=1740819080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=